146
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:14,700
♪Unable to sleep,  I was intoxicated
by the fragrance of books♪

147
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:18,340
♪With you,
the fragrance fills the sky together♪

148
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:24,220
♪Parting makes it hard
to express in many words♪

149
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:29,380
♪I use tears to grind
the residual moon into the inkstone♪

150
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:33,020
♪To write my longing
into every word and line♪

151
